title: CAPONE Ending Explained and Real Life Comparison!
author: Think Story
comment: Needed more grunting and shitting tbh

description:
In this video we take a look at Josh Trank's new mobster film "Capone" starring Tom Hardy, Matt Dillon, and Linda Cardellini. I break down the ending, compare its real life mobsters, and deep dive into its symbolism.
